snippet.title: Delta Force: Hawk Ops - Official Deep Dive Trailer | gamescom 2023
snippet.description: Join members of the development team of Delta Force: Hawk Ops for a deep dive into the upcoming tactical shooter game, including a peek at the variety of playable operators, the art design and inspiration, the reveal of Black Hawk Down as a single-player campaign mode, and much more. Delta Force: Hawk Ops will be available on PlayStation, Xbox, Steam, Epic Games Store, and mobile.
